               <p>CHARLES LOW. I am an under gardener to Mr. Rothschild. I know that the cloth was on the table on the 2d of May.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240603-54-person496">
                  LEONARD 
                  MATTHEWS
               <interp inst="t18240603-54-person496" type="surname" value="MATTHEWS"></interp>
